text: Carina Harache (born 6 February 1984) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand women's national water polo team. She played at the 2007 World Aquatics Championships, 2009 World Aquatics Championships, 2011 World Aquatics Championships, and 2010 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup. == References == == Other websites == * Carina Harache of New Zealand reacts Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
